{"tid":398763,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"近排訓覺不斷發夢","createTime":"2017-09-13T12:12:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-31T08:19:31.000Z","uid":943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"aa5159dfe733aa2f53b2ba31e82feab22df04116","tid":398763,"uid":943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T12:12:30.000Z","msg":"以前訓覺都會發，但都唔會係咁發夢<br />\n近排唔知做咩係好多夢，仲要都幾記得啲夢境，平時一醒就唔記得架嘛<br />\n啲夢好真，但係唔係惡夢嚟唔係俾鬼追嗰啲<br />\n好困擾，係咁發夢發到好似冇訓過咁，醒咗仲要分吓真定假同埋冇乜精神<br />\n琴晚發夢夢見呀哥同爸爸死咗，我醒咗都要分真假因為醒嗰陣個人真係喊緊，個人要平伏吓諗清楚自己係咪醒咗先得<br />\n唔知點解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f22322a204f7a39135a82ece1624f2458e5f022","tid":398763,"uid":943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T12:18:04.000Z","msg":"有冇人都好似我咁啊，或者話我知代表咩"},{"pid":"47b451c7d00faaf1080c82e23d57730c3ea1e930","tid":398763,"uid":943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T12:21:47.000Z","msg":"冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f09df477b95a8fe55dda2b3c771ec42f99a40baa","tid":398763,"uid":96486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T12:38:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我日日都發幾個夢，好慘"},{"pid":"996d3f1bb7ee6b0f1503d59429ab2bbc11e8782b","tid":398763,"uid":73109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T12:40:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"355b652bc2dc75908fde97aa0d5791cb47128796","tid":398763,"uid":92456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T12:48:57.000Z","msg":"都係反映緊你嘅潛意識<br />\n我基本上冇一晚係唔發夢，但身邊朋友都唔會咁"},{"pid":"c2daf484a102e739c377330766d39d68a9f0b3ac","tid":398763,"uid":47660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T12:54:14.000Z","msg":"日日都發啲比人追殺逃走嘅夢<br />\n又有啲係兩隊人咁玩遊戲，但都係輪流追殺嘅夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  啲場境仲要好似好科幻好真實，好似真係存在咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\